    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait really?? i read online that as long as you don't take too much of the supplement it's fine. like, if i just take a small dose of the St. Johns Wort once a day, it shouldn't really interfere with the sertraline much, right? i'm just really struggling with the brain fog and need something to help me get through finals week.",
